snippet.title: [Dev. Log] Peaceful Soul - Fishing System and Spot
snippet.description:
#peacefulsoul #radishdeveloper #indiegame #indiegamedev
We attempted to create a fishing place in Radish Village this time. There are currently only two fishing sites (till this video was filmed), but there will be roughly five in the future.

Here's a sneak peek at Peaceful Soul's fishing mechanism. Please have pleasure in it.
